pageProduct.name: Swisse Ultibiotic Daily Immune Probiotic 30 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultibiotic Daily Immune Probiotic is a premium quality formula combining two clinically trialled strains- Lactobacillus plantarum (HEAL 9) and Lactobacillus paracasei (8700:2)-specifically formulated to:



  • Reduce and relieve the severity of common cold symptoms including runny nose, nasal congestion and sore throat

  • Shorten the duration of colds and support a healthy recovery

  • Maintain a healthy immune system to fight illness

  • Help stimulate a healthy immune system response.

Size: 30 Pack

Warnings

If symptoms persist, consult your healthcare practitioner.

IMPORTANT INFORMATION

No added lactose, gluten, yeast, egg, soy, artificial colours or artificial flavours.

Gluten free and dairy free.

Ingredients

EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS:
Lactobacillus plantarum (HEAL 9) 500 million CFU
Lactobacillus paracasei (8700:2) 500 million CFU

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
One capsule daily, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C.

Do not use if cap seal is broken.
